data.description: So much to love in this gorgeous, immaculate, impeccably maintained Beaverbrooke ranch home! Warm, inviting covered entry opens up to open concept living room with gas fireplace. 3 good sized bedrooms on the main level include a large master with walkin closet and en suite with shower. Updated kitchen and dining area look over living area. Dining area walks out to beautiful deck and fenced backyard for outdoor entertaining. Lower level is perfect for family gatherings with dining area, huge living space and bar as well as 4th bedroom and additional bathroom! This home is right in the heart of Grimes with easy access to the interstate and tons of amenities! This is your forever home, come check it out today!
